<inglise> COUNCIL REGULATION (EEC) No 193/82 of 26 January 1982 laying down general rules for transfers of quotas in the sugar sector </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 193/82, millega s&auml;testatakse suhkrusektori kvootide &uuml;lekandmise &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad 26. jaanuar 1982 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 of 3 June 1981 on the common organization of the markets in the sugar sector (1), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 192/82 (4), and in particular Article 25 (4) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1981. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 suhkrusektori turgude &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 192/82, (2) eriti selle artikli 25 l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 25 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 lays down that Member States may transfer A quotas and B quotas between undertakings, taking into consideration the interests of each of the parties concerned, and in particular those of sugar-beet or sugar-cane producers; whereas, moreover, Article 25 (4) provides that general rules are to be adopted concerning the adjustment of quotas, in particular in the event of a merger or transfer of undertakings; whereas the incorporation of such a possibility in an inter-trade agreement would facilitate the use of this authorization by the Member State concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 25 l&otilde;ikes 1 on s&auml;testatud, et liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad A- ja B-kvoote ettev&otilde;tjate vahel &uuml;le kanda, v&otilde;ttes arvesse k&otilde;igi asjaomaste poolte, eelk&otilde;ige suhkrupeedi ja suhkruroo tootjate huvisid; peale selle on artikli 25 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud, et tuleb vastu v&otilde;tta kvootide kohandamist k&auml;sitlevad &uuml;ldeeskirjad, eriti ettev&otilde;tjate &uuml;hinemise v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randamise korral; sellise v&otilde;imaluse lisamine majandusharusisesesse kokkuleppesse h&otilde;lbustaks asjaomastel liikmesriikidel k&otilde;nealust luba kasutada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas A quotas and B quotas are affected following a merger or transfer of undertakings, a transfer by an undertaking of one of its factories or the closure of an undertaking or one of its factories; whereas, therefore, conditions should be laid down for the adjustment by Member States of the quotas of the undertakings in question; </inglise>
<eesti> A- ja B-kvoote m&otilde;jutab ettev&otilde;tjate &uuml;hinemine v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randmine, ettev&otilde;tja &uuml;he vabriku v&otilde;&otilde;randamine, ettev&otilde;tja tegevuse l&otilde;petamine v&otilde;i &uuml;he tema vabriku sulgemine; seep&auml;rast tuleks s&auml;testada tingimused k&otilde;nealuste ettev&otilde;tete kvootide kohandamiseks liikmesriikide poolt; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is essential that the adjustment of the quotas of sugar-producing undertakings should not damage the interests of the sugar-beet or sugar-cane producers concerned; whereas the Member States should be authorized to allocate quotas to undertakings other than those directly concerned where some of the beet or cane producers directly affected by a merger, transfer or closure expressly show their willingness to supply their beet or their cane to a given undertaking; </inglise>
<eesti> on oluline, et suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tete kvootide kohandamine ei kahjustaks asjaomaste suhkrupeedi ja suhkruroo tootjate huvisid; liikmesriikidel peaks olema lubatud eraldada kvoote ettev&otilde;tjatele, mis ei ole asjaga otseselt seotud, kui m&otilde;ni suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i suhkruroo tootja, keda &uuml;hinemine, v&otilde;&otilde;randamine, tegevuse l&otilde;petamine v&otilde;i vabriku sulgemine otseselt m&otilde;jutab, avaldab selgelt soovi tarnida oma suhkrupeeti v&otilde;i -roogu asjaomasele ettev&otilde;tjale; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the second subparagraph of Article 25 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 authorizes Italy, and France as regards the French overseas departments, to adjust the quotas of undertakings without applying the 10 % limit where such transfers are made on the basis of restructuring plans in the beet or cane and sugar manufacturing sectors; whereas, in order to make implementation of such restructuring plans effective, Italy and France as regards the said departments, should be allowed, subject to certain conditions, to regard a group of undertakings as a sugar-producing undertaking; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 25 l&otilde;ike 2 teise l&otilde;igu kohaselt on Itaalial ja Prantsusmaal seoses Prantsuse &uuml;lemeredepartemangudega lubatud kohandada ettev&otilde;tjate kvoote, kohaldamata 10% piirangut, kui sellised &uuml;lekandmised tehakse suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i suhkruroo ja suhkrutootmissektori &uuml;mberkorralduskavade alusel; selliste &uuml;mberkorralduskavade rakendamise t&otilde;hustamiseks tuleks Itaalial ja Prantsusmaal seoses eespool nimetatud departemangudega lubada teatavatel tingimustel k&auml;sitada ettev&otilde;tjate r&uuml;hma suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjana; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas for certain operations relating to isoglucose-producing undertakings, rules which tally with those applicable to sugar should be laid down; </inglise>
<eesti> isogl&uuml;koositootmisettev&otilde;tjatega seotud teatavate toimingute kohta tuleks s&auml;testada eeskirjad, mis oleksid koosk&otilde;las suhkru suhtes kohaldatavate eeskirjadega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas measures taken by the Member States affecting quotas should be communicated to the Commission in order to be able to take effect; </inglise>
<eesti> liikmesriikide v&otilde;etud meetmetest, mis m&otilde;jutavad kvoote, tuleks nende j&otilde;ustumise v&otilde;imaldamiseks teatada komisjonile; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Council Regulation (EEC) No 3331/74 of 19 December 1974 on the allocation and alteration of the basic quotas for sugar (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81, and Council Regulation (EEC) No 748/68 of 18 June 1968 on laying down general rules for postponing part of the sugar production to the following marketing year (4), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2829/71 (5), should be repealed, </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks tunnistada kehtetuks n&otilde;ukogu 19. detsembri 1974. aasta m&auml;&auml;rus (EM&Uuml;) nr 3331/74 suhkru p&otilde;hikvootide jagamise ja muutmise kohta, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81, ja n&otilde;ukogu 18. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rus (EM&Uuml;) nr 746/68, millega s&auml;testatakse &uuml;ldeeskirjad suhkrutoodangu osa &uuml;lekandmiseks j&auml;rgmisesse majandusaastasse, (4) muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2829/71; (5) </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall adopt such measures as they deem necessary to take account of the interests of sugar-beet and sugar-cane producers in the event of allocation of quotas to a sugar-producing undertaking having more than one factory. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid v&otilde;tavad vastu meetmed, mida nad peavad vajalikuks suhkrupeedi ja suhkruroo tootjate huvide arvessev&otilde;tmiseks juhul, kui kvoodid kantakse &uuml;le suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjale, kellel on mitu vabrikut. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> In the event of the merger or transfer of sugar-producing undertakings and in the event of the transfer of sugar factories, the A and B quotas shall, without prejudice, to paragraph 2, be adjusted as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> Suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tete &uuml;hinemise v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randamise ja suhkruvabrikute v&otilde;&otilde;randamise korral kohandatakse A- ja B-kvoote j&auml;rgmiselt, ilma et see piiraks l&otilde;ike 2 kohaldamist: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) in the event of the merger of sugar-producing undertakings, the Member States shall allocate to the undertaking resulting from the merger an A quota and a B quota equal respectively to the sum </inglise>
<eesti> a) suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjate &uuml;hinemise korral m&auml;&auml;rab liikmesriik &uuml;hinemise tulemusel tekkinud ettev&otilde;tjale A- ja B-kvoodi, mis on v&otilde;rdsed vastavalt </eesti>
<inglise> of the A quotas and the sum of the B quotas allocated prior to the merger to the sugar-producing undertakings concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> A-kvoodi summaga ja B-kvoodi summaga, mis oli m&auml;&auml;ratud asjaomastele suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjatele enne &uuml;hinemist; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) in the event of the transfer of a sugar-producing undertaking, the Member State shall allocate to the transferee undertaking for the production of sugar the A quota and the B quota of the undertaking transferred or, if there is more than one transferee undertaking, the allocation shall be made in proportion to the sugar production absorbed by each of them; </inglise>
<eesti> b) suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;&otilde;randamise korral m&auml;&auml;rab liikmesriik v&otilde;&otilde;randatud ettev&otilde;tja A- ja B-kvoodi suhkru tootmiseks v&otilde;&otilde;randavale ettev&otilde;tjale v&otilde;i kui v&otilde;&otilde;randavaid ettev&otilde;tjaid on mitu, m&auml;&auml;ratakse kvoodid v&otilde;rdeliselt v&otilde;&otilde;randatud ettev&otilde;tja suhkrutoodangu mahuga; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) in the event of the transfer of a sugar factory, the Member State shall reduce the A quota and the B quota of the undertaking transferring ownership of the factory and shall increase the A quota and the B quota of the sugar-producing undertaking or undertakings purchasing the factory in question by the quantity deducted in proportion to the production absorbed. </inglise>
<eesti> c) suhkruvabriku v&otilde;&otilde;randamise korral v&auml;hendab liikmesriik selle ettev&otilde;tja A- ja B-kvooti, kes vabriku omandi &uuml;le annab, ja suurendab k&otilde;nealuse vabriku ostnud suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;i ettev&otilde;tjate A- ja B-kvooti, lisades mahaarvatud koguse v&otilde;rdeliselt v&otilde;&otilde;randatud vabriku tootmismahuga. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a number of the sugar-beet or cane producers directly affected by one of the operations referred to in paragraph 1 expressly show their willingness to supply their beet or cane to a sugar-producing undertaking which is not party to those operations, the Member State may make the allocation on the basis of the production absorbed by the undertaking to which they intend to supply their beet or cane. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui osa suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i suhkruroo tootjaid, keda otseselt m&otilde;jutab m&otilde;ni l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud toiming, avaldab selgelt soovi tarnida oma suhkrupeeti v&otilde;i -roogu suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjatele, kes ei osale k&otilde;nealustes toimingutes, v&otilde;ib liikmesriik m&auml;&auml;rata kvoodi ettev&otilde;tjale, kellele tootjad kavatsevad oma suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i -roo tarnida, vastavalt ettev&otilde;tja poolt v&otilde;&otilde;randatava ettev&otilde;tja tootmismahule. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> In the event of the closure, in circumstances other than those referred to in paragraph 1, of: </inglise>
<eesti> Kui muudel kui l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud asjaoludel l&otilde;petatakse: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) a sugar-producing undertaking, </inglise>
<eesti> a) suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tja tegevus, </eesti>
<inglise> (b) one or more factories of a sugar-producing undertaking, </inglise>
<eesti> b) suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tja &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitme vabriku tegevus, </eesti>
<inglise> the Member State may allocate the part of the quotas involved in such closure to one or more sugar-producing undertakings. </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ib liikmesriik m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealuse tegevuse l&otilde;petamisega seotud kvoodid &uuml;hele v&otilde;i mitmele suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjale. </eesti>
<inglise> The Member State may, also in the case referred to in (b) in the preceding subparagraph, where some of the producers concerned expressly show their willingness to supply their beet or cane to a given sugar-producing undertaking, allocate that proportion of the quotas which corresponds to the beet or sugar cane in question to the undertaking which they intend to supply with those products. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui osa tootjaid avaldab selgelt soovi tarnida oma suhkrupeeti v&otilde;i -roogu asjaomasele suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjale, v&otilde;ib liikmesriik (ka eelmise l&otilde;igu punktis b osutatud juhul) m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealusele suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i -roo kogusele vastava osa kvoote ettev&otilde;tjale, kellele tootjad kavatsevad need tooted tarnida. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the derogation referred to in Article 30 (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 is invoked, the Member State in question may require the beet producers and sugar manufacturers concerned by that derogation to incorporate in their inter-trade agreements special clauses for paragraphs 2 and 3 to be applied by that Member State where appropriate. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 30 l&otilde;ikes 3 osutatud erandi puhul v&otilde;ib k&otilde;nealune liikmesriik n&otilde;uda, et asjaomased suhkrupeedi tootjad ja suhkrutootjad lisaksid oma majandusharusisestesse kokkulepetesse eritingimused, et k&otilde;nealune liikmesriik saaks vajaduse korral kohaldada l&otilde;ikeid 2 ja 3. </eesti>
<inglise> 5. </inglise>
<eesti> 5. </eesti>
<inglise> In the event of the lease of a factory belonging to a sugar-producing undertaking, the Member State may reduce the quotas of the undertaking which offers the factory for rent and allocate the portion by which the quota was reduced to the undertaking which rents the factory in order to produce sugar in it. </inglise>
<eesti> Suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tja vabriku rentimise korral v&otilde;ib liikmesriik v&auml;hendada rendile andva ettev&otilde;tte kvoote, ning m&auml;&auml;rata kvoodist mahaarvatud osa ettev&otilde;tjale, kes v&otilde;tab vabriku rendile suhkru tootmise eesm&auml;rgil. </eesti>
<inglise> If the lease is terminated during the period of the three marketing years referred to in Article 5 (d), the adjustment of quotas pursuant to the preceding subparagraph shall be cancelled retroactively by the Member State as at the date on which the lease took effect. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui rendisuhe l&otilde;petatakse artikli 5 punktis d osutatud kolme majandusaasta jooksul, t&uuml;histab liikmesriik tagasiulatuvalt vastavalt eelmisele l&otilde;igule kehtestatud kvootide kohandamise alates rendisuhte j&otilde;ustumise kuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise> However, if the lease is terminated by reason of force majeure, the Member State shall not be bound to cancel the adjustment. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui rendisuhe l&otilde;peb v&auml;&auml;ramatu j&otilde;u t&otilde;ttu, ei ole liikmesriik kohustatud kohandamist t&uuml;histama. </eesti>
<inglise> 6. </inglise>
<eesti> 6. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a sugar-producing undertaking can no longer ensure that it meets its obligations under Community regulations towards the sugar-beet or sugar-cane producers concerned, and where that situation has been ascertained by the competent authorities of the Member State in question, the latter may allocate for one or more marketing years the part of the quotas involved to one or more sugar-producing undertakings in proportion to the production absorbed. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tja ei suuda enam tagada &uuml;henduse eeskirjadega etten&auml;htud kohustuste t&auml;itmist asjaomaste suhkrupeedi ja suhkruroo tootjate suhtes ning kui selle olukorra on kindlaks teinud k&otilde;nealuse liikmesriigi asjaomased asutused, v&otilde;ib liikmesriik m&auml;&auml;rata osa asjaomastest kvootidest &uuml;heks v&otilde;i mitmeks majandusaastaks &uuml;hele v&otilde;i mitmele suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjale v&otilde;rdeliselt v&otilde;&otilde;randatava ettev&otilde;tja tootmismahuga. </eesti>
<inglise> 7. </inglise>
<eesti> 7. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a sugar-producing undertaking is granted by the Member State price and outlet guarantees in respect of the processing of sugar beet into ethyl alcohol, the Member State may, in agreement with that undertaking and the sugar-beet producers concerned, allocate for one or more marketing years all or part of the sugar-production quotas to one or more other undertakings. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui liikmesriik on andnud suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjale hinna- ja turustustagatisi seoses suhkrupeedi t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisega et&uuml;&uuml;lalkoholiks, v&otilde;ib liikmesriik kokkuleppel k&otilde;nealuse ettev&otilde;tja ja asjaomaste suhkrupeeditootjatega m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;ik suhkrutootmiskvoodid v&otilde;i osa neist &uuml;heks v&otilde;i mitmeks majandusaastaks &uuml;hele v&otilde;i mitmele teisele ettev&otilde;tjale. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> In the event of the merger or transfer of isoglucose-producing undertakings, in the event of the transfer of an isoglucose-producing factory and in the event of the closure of one or more isoglucose-producing undertakings, the Member State may allocate the quotas in question for the production of isoglucose to one or more undertakings whether or not they have a production quota. </inglise>
<eesti> Isogl&uuml;koositootmisettev&otilde;tjate &uuml;hinemise v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randamise, isogl&uuml;koositootmisvabriku &uuml;leandmise ja &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitme isogl&uuml;koositootmisettev&otilde;tja tegevuse l&otilde;petamise korral v&otilde;ib liikmesriik m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealused kvoodid isogl&uuml;koosi tootmiseks &uuml;hele v&otilde;i mitmele ettev&otilde;tjale, s&otilde;ltumata sellest, kas neil on tootmiskvoot. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> Without prejudice to Article 8, the measures, taken pursuant to Article 2 and Article 3, may take effect only if: </inglise>
<eesti> Ilma et see piiraks artikli 8 kohaldamist, v&otilde;ib vastavalt artiklitele 2 ja 3 v&otilde;etud meetmeid j&otilde;ustada ainult juhul, kui: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the interests of each of the parties concerned are taken into consideration, and </inglise>
<eesti> a) k&otilde;igi asjaomaste poolte huvisid on arvesse v&otilde;etud, </eesti>
<inglise> (b) the Member State concerned considers them to be such as to improve the structure of the beet, cane and sugar-manufacturing sectors, and </inglise>
<eesti> b) asjaomase liikmesriigi arvates parandavad need suhkrupeedi-, suhkruroo- ja suhkrutootmissektorite struktuuri ja </eesti>
<inglise> (c) they concern undertakings established in the same region within the meaning of Article 24 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81. </inglise>
<eesti> c) need on seotud ettev&otilde;tjatega, kes asuvad samas piirkonnas m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 24 l&otilde;ike 2 t&auml;henduses. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purpose of this Regulation: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses kasutatakse j&auml;rgmiseid m&otilde;isteid: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) 'merger of undertakings' means the consolidation into a single undertaking of two or more undertakings; </inglise>
<eesti> a) ettev&otilde;tjate &uuml;hinemine - kahe v&otilde;i enama ettev&otilde;tte &uuml;hendamine &uuml;heks ettev&otilde;tteks; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) 'transfer of an undertaking' means the transfer or absorption of the assets of an undertaking having quotas to one or more undertakings; </inglise>
<eesti> b) ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;&otilde;randamine - kvoote omava ettev&otilde;tte varade omandi &uuml;leandmine v&otilde;i &uuml;leminek &uuml;hele v&otilde;i mitmele ettev&otilde;ttele; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) 'transfer of a factory' means the transfer of ownership of a technical unit, including all the plant required to manufacture the product in question, to one or more undertakings, resulting in the partial or total absorption of the production of the undertaking making the transfer; </inglise>
<eesti> c) vabriku v&otilde;&otilde;randamine - &uuml;hele v&otilde;i mitmele ettev&otilde;tjale sellise tehnilise &uuml;ksuse omandi&otilde;iguse &uuml;leandmine, milles on k&otilde;nealuse toote valmistamiseks vajalik sisseseade, ja mille tulemuseks on v&otilde;&otilde;randatava ettev&otilde;tja tootmise osaline v&otilde;i t&auml;ielik &uuml;leminek; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) 'lease of a factory' means the leasehold contract of a technical unit including all the plant required for the manufacture of sugar, with a view to its operation, concluded for a period of at least three consecutive marketing years, which the parties agree not to terminate before the end of the third marketing year, with an undertaking which is established in the same region, within the meaning of Article 24 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81, as the factory in question, if, after the lease takes effect, the undertaking which rents the factory can be considered a solely sugar-producing undertaking for its entire production. </inglise>
<eesti> d) vabriku rentimine - sellise tehnilise &uuml;ksuse rendileping, mille juurde kuulub suhkrutootmiseks vajalik sisseseade, kusjuures rendileping s&otilde;lmitakse vabriku tegevust arvestades v&auml;hemalt kolmeks j&auml;rjestikuseks majandusaastaks ettev&otilde;tjaga, kes asub k&otilde;nealuse vabrikuga samas piirkonnas m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 24 l&otilde;ike 2 t&auml;henduses, kui vabriku rendile v&otilde;tnud ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;ib p&auml;rast rendisuhte tekkimist kogu toodangu alusel k&auml;sitada &uuml;he suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjana, kusjuures pooled kohustuvad lepingut enne kolmanda majandusaasta l&otilde;ppu mitte l&otilde;petama. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> The measures referred to in Articles 2 and 3 shall take effect when the closure of the undertaking or factory, the merger or transfer occurs: </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklis 2 ja artiklis 3 osutatud meetmed j&otilde;ustuvad, kui ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;i vabriku tegevuse l&otilde;petamine, &uuml;hinemine v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randamine toimub: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) between 1 July and 31 January of the following year, for the marketing year current during that period; </inglise>
<eesti> a) 1. juuli ja j&auml;rgmise aasta 31. jaanuari vahel selles ajavahemikus jooksva majandusaasta osas; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) between 1 February and 30 June of the same year, for the marketing year following that period. </inglise>
<eesti> b) sama aasta 1. veebruari ja 30. juuni vahel sellele ajavahemikule j&auml;rgneva majandusaasta osas. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> Where a Member State applies Article 25 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81, it shall allocate the adjusted quotas before 1 March with a view to applying them in the following marketing year. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui liikmesriik kohaldab m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 25 l&otilde;iget 2, m&auml;&auml;rab ta kohandatud kvoodid enne 1. m&auml;rtsi, et neid saaks kohaldada j&auml;rgmisel majandusaastal. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For the marketing years 1982/83 to 1985/86: </inglise>
<eesti> Majandusaastateks 1982/83-1985/86: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) measures taken by a Member State pursuant to Article 25 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 and Articles 2 and 3 of this Regulation may not take effect until they have been communicated to the Commission within the time limits stipulated and the Member State has adopted the appropriate measures for the corresponding transfer of the minimum stock obligations; </inglise>
<eesti> a) v&otilde;ib liikmesriikide poolt vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 25 l&otilde;ikele 2 ja k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artiklitele 2 ja 3 v&otilde;etud meetmeid j&otilde;ustada p&auml;rast seda, kui nendest on etten&auml;htud aja jooksul teatatud komisjonile ja liikmesriik on v&otilde;tnud asjakohased meetmed miinimumvaruga seotud kohustuste vastavaks &uuml;lekandmiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) Member States shall inform the Commission, not later than 15 days after the allocation referred to in Article 7 of the adjusted A and B quotas. </inglise>
<eesti> b) liikmesriik teatab komisjonile kohandatud A- ja B-kvoodid hiljemalt 15 p&auml;eva jooksul p&auml;rast artiklis 7 osutatud m&auml;&auml;ramist. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Where Articles 2 and 3 are applied, Member States shall inform the Commission, not later than 15 days following expiry of the periods referred to in Article 6 of the adjusted A and B quotas. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui kohaldatakse artikleid 2 ja 3, teatavad liikmesriigid komisjonile kohandatud A- ja B-kvoodid hiljemalt 15 p&auml;eva jooksul p&auml;rast artiklis 6 osutatud ajavahemike l&otilde;ppu. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 9 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 9 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of transfers of quotas in Italy and in the French overseas departments under the restructuring plans referred to in the second subparagraph of Article 25 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81, a group of sugar-producing undertakings having technical, economic and structural links and jointly and severally liable for their obligations, particularly in respect of beet growers or cane growers, under Community rules may be regarded as a sugar-producing undertaking. </inglise>
<eesti> Kvootide &uuml;lekandmiseks Itaalias ja Prantsuse &uuml;lemeredepartemangudes m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 25 l&otilde;ike 2 teises l&otilde;igus osutatud &uuml;mberkorralduskava raames v&otilde;ib suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjate r&uuml;hma, kes on tehniliselt, majanduslikult ja struktuuriliselt seotud ning kes vastutavad solidaarselt oma kohustuste eest, eelk&otilde;ige suhkrupeedi ja -roo kasvatajate suhtes, vastavalt &uuml;henduse eeskirjadele k&auml;sitada &uuml;he suhkrutootmisettev&otilde;tjana. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 10 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 10 </eesti>
<inglise> Regulations (EEC) No 3331/74 and (EEC) No 748/68 are hereby repealed. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;rused (EM&Uuml;) nr 3331/74 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 748/68 tunnistatakse kehtetuks. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 11 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 11 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
